/*
  ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
  ║              StudyMate  Firmware  v5.0                   ║
  ║     ESP32 + I2C 20x4 LCD + DS3231 OR ESP32 Hotspot       ║
  ╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
  ║  WIRING                                                  ║
  ║  LCD  SDA -> GPIO 4    SCL -> GPIO 16                    ║
  ║  RTC  SDA -> GPIO 4    SCL -> GPIO 16  (optional)        ║
  ║  BTN_A -> GPIO 27                                        ║
  ║  BTN_B -> GPIO 26   (long press = back/quit)             ║
  ╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
  ║  LIBRARIES  (Arduino Library Manager)                    ║
  ║  - LiquidCrystal I2C  by Frank de Brabander              ║
  ║  - RTClib              by Adafruit                       ║
  ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

  ── CUSTOM CHARACTER SLOTS ────────────────────────────────────
  The HD44780 LCD has 8 user-definable 5x8 pixel characters.
  Slots 0-4 are loaded at boot and never change.
  Slots 5-7 are hot-swapped per screen for the hint row icons.

  Permanent (boot):
    #0  ██  Solid bar  — progress fill
    #1  □   Outline bar — progress empty
    #2  ▶   Play arrow  — running state / menu cursor
    #3  ⏸   Pause bars  — paused state
    #4  ♥   Heart       — splash & done screens

  Hot-swapped into slots 5-7 before each hint row draw:
    ↕   Up-down scroll  (menus: A scrolls)
    ↓   Down / cycle    (session select: A cycles down)
    ↵   Enter/confirm   (B selects/starts)
    ←   Back arrow      (B long = go back)
    ⌂   Home icon       (B long = go home on timers)
    ♪   Music note      (exercise header)
    ✓   Checkmark       (sync done)
    ⊙   Clock face      (home screen header)
*/

